crowd,"},{"kind":"text","text":" none of their wealth,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and none of the eminent "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, Syr, Vg read and no rest"},{"kind":"text","text":" among them."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 73:8","book":"Psa","chapter":73,"verse":8},{"label":"Ps 125:3","book":"Psa","chapter":125,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, Syr, Vg read and no rest"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The time has come; the day has arrived."},{"kind":"text","text":" Let the buyer not rejoice "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 20:14","book":"Pro","chapter":20,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the seller not mourn,"},{"kind":"text","text":" for wrath is on her whole crowd. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 24:2","book":"Isa","chapter":24,"verse":2,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 20:14","book":"Pro","chapter":20,"verse":14},{"label":"Is 24:2","book":"Isa","chapter":24,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The seller will certainly not return"},{"kind":"text","text":" to what was sold"},{"kind":"text","text":" as long as he and the buyer remain alive. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit sold, while still in life is their life"},{"kind":"text","text":" For the vision concerning her whole crowd"},{"kind":"text","text":" will not be revoked,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and because of the iniquity of each one,"},{"kind":"text","text":" none will preserve his life."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit sold, while still in life is their life"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They have blown the trumpet "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 10:9","book":"Num","chapter":10,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and prepared everything,"},{"kind":"text","text":" but no one goes to war,"},{"kind":"text","text":" for my wrath is on her whole crowd."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 10:9","book":"Num","chapter":10,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The sword is on the outside; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 14:18","book":"Jer","chapter":14,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 6:11–12","book":"Ezk","chapter":6,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" plague and famine are on the inside."},{"kind":"text","text":" Whoever is in the field will die by the sword,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and famine and plague will devour"},{"kind":"text","text":" whoever is in the city."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 14:18","book":"Jer","chapter":14,"verse":18},{"label":"Ezk 6:11–12","book":"Ezk","chapter":6,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The survivors among them will escape "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 6:8","book":"Ezk","chapter":6,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 14:22","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and live on the mountains."},{"kind":"text","text":" Like doves of the valley,"},{"kind":"text","text":" all of them will moan,"},{"kind":"text","text":" each over his own iniquity."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 6:8","book":"Ezk","chapter":6,"verse":8},{"label":"Ezk 14:22","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"All their hands will become weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and all their knees will run with urine. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit knees will go water"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 13:7","book":"Isa","chapter":13,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 21:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":21,"verse":7,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 13:7","book":"Isa","chapter":13,"verse":7},{"label":"Ezk 21:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":21,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit knees will go water"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They will put on sackcloth,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and horror will overwhelm them."},{"kind":"text","text":" Shame will cover all their faces,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and all their heads will be bald. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 15:2–3","book":"Isa","chapter":15,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 8:10","book":"Amo","chapter":8,"verse":10,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 15:2–3","book":"Isa","chapter":15,"verse":2},{"label":"Am 8:10","book":"Amo","chapter":8,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They will throw their silver into the streets,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and their gold will seem like something filthy. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 2:20","book":"Isa","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 30:22","book":"Isa","chapter":30,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Their silver and gold will be unable to save them"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the day of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s wrath. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 11:4","book":"Pro","chapter":11,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zp 1:18","book":"Zep","chapter":1,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" They will not satisfy their appetites"},{"kind":"text","text":" or fill their stomachs,"},{"kind":"text","text":" for these were the stumbling blocks "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 14:3","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" that brought about their iniquity."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 2:20","book":"Isa","chapter":2,"verse":20},{"label":"Is 30:22","book":"Isa","chapter":30,"verse":22},{"label":"Pr 11:4","book":"Pro","chapter":11,"verse":4},{"label":"Zp 1:18","book":"Zep","chapter":1,"verse":18},{"label":"Ezk 14:3","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He appointed his beautiful ornaments for majesty,"},{"kind":"text","text":" but "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or They turned their beautiful ornaments into objects of pride, and"},{"kind":"text","text":" they made their detestable images from them,"},{"kind":"text","text":" their abhorrent things. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:30","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":30,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 16:17","book":"Ezk","chapter":16,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Therefore, I have made these"},{"kind":"text","text":" into something filthy to them."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 7:30","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":30},{"label":"Ezk 16:17","book":"Ezk","chapter":16,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or They turned their beautiful ornaments into objects of pride, and"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will hand these things over"},{"kind":"text","text":" to foreigners as plunder "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 24:13","book":"2Ki","chapter":24,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and to the wicked of the earth as spoil,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and they will profane them."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 24:13","book":"2Ki","chapter":24,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will turn my face from them"},{"kind":"text","text":" as they profane my treasured place."},{"kind":"text","text":" Violent men will enter it and profane it."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Forge the chain, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 27:2","book":"Jer","chapter":27,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the land is filled with crimes of bloodshed,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the city is filled with violence. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 8:17","book":"Ezk","chapter":8,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 9:9","book":"Ezk","chapter":9,"verse":9,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 27:2","book":"Jer","chapter":27,"verse":2},{"label":"Ezk 8:17","book":"Ezk","chapter":8,"verse":17},{"label":"Ezk 9:9","book":"Ezk","chapter":9,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So I will bring the most evil of nations "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 21:31","book":"Ezk","chapter":21,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 28:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":28,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to take possession of their houses."},{"kind":"text","text":" I will put an end to the pride of the strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and their sacred places will be profaned. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 7:20","book":"2Ch","chapter":7,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 24:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":24,"verse":21,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 21:31","book":"Ezk","chapter":21,"verse":31},{"label":"Ezk 28:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":28,"verse":7},{"label":"2Ch 7:20","book":"2Ch","chapter":7,"verse":20},{"label":"Ezk 24:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":24,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Anguish is coming!"},{"kind":"text","text":" They will look for peace, but there will be none."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Disaster after disaster will come, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 47:11","book":"Isa","chapter":47,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 4:20","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and there will be rumor after rumor. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 21:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":21,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Then they will look for a vision from a prophet, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 21:2","book":"Jer","chapter":21,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 37:17","book":"Jer","chapter":37,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" but instruction will perish from the priests"},{"kind":"text","text":" and counsel from the elders. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 74:9","book":"Psa","chapter":74,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mc 3:6","book":"Mic","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 47:11","book":"Isa","chapter":47,"verse":11},{"label":"Jr 4:20","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":20},{"label":"Ezk 21:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":21,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 21:2","book":"Jer","chapter":21,"verse":2},{"label":"Jr 37:17","book":"Jer","chapter":37,"verse":17},{"label":"Ps 74:9","book":"Psa","chapter":74,"verse":9},{"label":"Mc 3:6","book":"Mic","chapter":3,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:7:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The king will mourn;"},{"kind":"text","text":" the prince will be clothed in grief;"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the hands of the people of the land will tremble."},{"kind":"text","text":" I will deal with them according to their own conduct,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and I will judge them by their own standards. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:2","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Then they will know that I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 7:2","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279577322}